abel=\"Open menu\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"7\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"7\"></line><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"17\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"17\"></line></svg></button></div></nav></header><main><div style=\"background:var(--green-deep);padding:1rem 2rem 4rem;color:var(--cream)\"><div class=\"section-inner\"><div class=\"section-tag\" style=\"color:var(--gold);border-top-color:var(--gold)\">Membership</div><h1 class=\"section-h2\" style=\"color:var(--cream);font-size:clamp(1.75rem,4vw,2.75rem);margin-bottom:1rem\">Membership <em style=\"color:var(--gold);font-style:italic\">Application</em></h1><p style=\"font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:rgba(245,240,232,.72);max-width:540px;line-height:1.7\">For those who have already visited the Club and met or played with at least two Committee Members.</p></div></div><div style=\"background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(45,90,61,.07)\"><div class=\"section-inner\" style=\"padding:4rem 2rem 5rem\"><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:minmax(0,1.8fr) minmax(0,1fr);gap:2rem;align-items:start\"><form style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.25rem\"><style>\n        .appform-input:focus { border-color: var(--gold) !important; }\n        .appform-enquiry-btn:hover { background: rgba(168,149,96,0.1) !important; }\n        .appform-submit-btn:hover:not(:disabled) { background: #6b5519 !important; }\n      </style><div style=\"background:rgba(168,149,96,0.06);border-left:4px solid var(--gold);padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;border-radius:4px;margin-bottom:0.75rem\"><p style=\"font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:var(--green-deep);line-height:1.7;margin:0\">This form is for applicants who have already visited the Club and met or played with at least two Committee Members. If you have not yet visited, please start with an enquiry first.</p><a href=\"/apply\" class=\"appform-enquiry-btn\" style=\"display:inline-block;margin-top:1rem;background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--gold);color:var(--gold);padding:0.6rem 1.25rem;border-radius:4px;font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;transition:background 0.15s\">Not yet visited? Make an Enquiry →</a></div><h3 style=\"font-family:&#x27;Playfair Display&#x27;, serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:var(--green-deep);margin-top:2rem;margin-bottom:1rem\">Your Details</h3><div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column\"><label style=\"display:block;font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--green-deep);margin-bottom:6px\">Full Name <span style=\"color:var(--gold);margin-left:2px\">*</span></label><input type=\"text\" required=\"\" autoComplete=\"name\" class=\"appform-input\" style=\"width:100%;padding:11px 14px;border:1px solid rgba(45,90,61,.22);background:#fff;font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:var(--green-deep);outline:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:2px;appearance:none;-webkit-appearance:none\" name=\"full_name\"/></div><div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column\"><label style=\"display:block;font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--green-deep);margin-bottom:6px\">Date of Birth <span style=\"color:var(--gold);margin-left:2px\">*</span></label><input type=\"date\" required=\"\" class=\"appform-input\" style=\"width:100%;padding:11px 14px;border:1px solid rgba(45,90,61,.22);background:#fff;font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:var(--green-deep);outline:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:2px;appearance:none;-webkit-appearance:none\" name=\"dob\"/></div><div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column\"><label style=\"display:block;font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--green-deep);margin-bottom:6px\">Email Address <span style=\"color:var(--gold);margin-left:2px\">*</span></label><input type=\"email\" required=\"\" autoComplete=\"email\" class=\"appform-input\" style=\"width:100%;padding:11px 14px;border:1px solid rgba(45,90,61,.22);background:#fff;font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:var(--green-deep);outline:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:2px;appearance:none;-webkit-appearance:none\" name=\"email\"/></div><div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column\"><label style=\"display:block;font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--green-deep);margin-bottom:6px\">Phone Number <span style=\"color:var(--gold);margin-left:2px\">*</span></label><input type=\"tel\" required=\"\" autoComplete=\"tel\" class=\"appform-input\" style=\"width:100%;padding:11px 14px;border:1px solid rgba(45,90,61,.22);background:#fff;font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:var(--green-deep);outline:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:2px;appearance:none;-webkit-appearance:none\" name=\"phone\"/></div><div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column\"><label style=\"display:block;font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--green-deep);margin-bottom:6px\">Address <span style=\"color:var(--gold);margin-left:2px\">*</span></label><textarea name=\"address\" rows=\"3\" required=\"\" autoComplete=\"street-address\" class=\"appform-input\" style=\"width:100%;padding:11px 14px;border:1px solid rgba(45,90,61,.22);background:#fff;font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:var(--green-deep);outline:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:2px;appearance:none;-webkit-appearance:none;resize:vertical;line-height:1.6\"></textarea></div><div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column\"><label style=\"display:block;font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--green-deep);margin-bottom:6px\">Are you rejoining the Club? <span style=\"color:var(--gold);margin-left:2px\">*</span></label><div style=\"display:flex;gap:1.75rem;margin-top:4px\"><label style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:var(--green-deep);cursor:pointer;font-weight:normal\"><input type=\"radio\" required=\"\" style=\"accent-color:var(--gold);width:16px;height:16px;cursor:pointer;flex-shrink:0\" name=\"rejoining\" value=\"yes\"/>Yes</label><label style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:var(--green-deep);cursor:pointer;font-weight:normal\"><input type=\"radio\" required=\"\" style=\"accent-color:var(--gold);width:16px;height:16px;cursor:pointer;flex-shrink:0\" name=\"rejoining\" value=\"no\"/>No</label></div></div><h3 style=\"font-family:&#x27;Playfair Display&#x27;, serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:var(--green-deep);margin-top:2rem;margin-bottom:1rem\">Your Visit</h3><div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column\"><label style=\"display:block;font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--green-deep);margin-bottom:6px\">Names of the two Committee Members you have met or played with <span style=\"color:var(--gold);margin-left:2px\">*</span></label><p style=\"font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:italic;color:rgba(45,90,61,0.7);margin:0 0 6px\">Please give both names so we can match your application to your visit.</p><textarea name=\"committee_members\" rows=\"2\" required=\"\" class=\"appform-input\" style=\"width:100%;padding:11px 14px;border:1px solid rgba(45,90,61,.22);background:#fff;font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:var(--green-deep);outline:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:2px;appearance:none;-webkit-appearance:none;resize:vertical;line-height:1.6\"></textarea></div><div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column\"><label style=\"display:block;font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--green-deep);margin-bottom:6px\">Approximate date of your visit</label><input type=\"date\" class=\"appform-input\" style=\"width:100%;padding:11px 14px;border:1px solid rgba(45,90,61,.22);background:#fff;font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:var(--green-deep);outline:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:2px;appearance:none;-webkit-appearance:none\" name=\"visit_date\"/></div><h3 style=\"font-family:&#x27;Playfair Display&#x27;, serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:var(--green-deep);margin-top:2rem;margin-bottom:1rem\">Proposer Details</h3><p style=\"font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:italic;color:rgba(45,90,61,0.7);margin:-0.5rem 0 0\">Please give the names of the two current members who are proposing and seconding your application.</p><div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column\"><label style=\"display:block;font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--green-deep);margin-bottom:6px\">Proposer Name <span style=\"color:var(--gold);margin-left:2px\">*</span></label><input type=\"text\" required=\"\" class=\"appform-input\" style=\"width:100%;padding:11px 14px;border:1px solid rgba(45,90,61,.22);background:#fff;font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:var(--green-deep);outline:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:2px;appearance:none;-webkit-appearance:none\" name=\"proposer_name\"/></div><div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column\"><label style=\"display:block;font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--green-deep);margin-bottom:6px\">Seconder Name <span style=\"color:var(--gold);margin-left:2px\">*</span></label><input type=\"text\" required=\"\" class=\"appform-input\" style=\"width:100%;padding:11px 14px;border:1px solid rgba(45,90,61,.22);background:#fff;font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:var(--green-deep);outline:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:2px;appearance:none;-webkit-appearance:none\" name=\"seconder_name\"/></div><h3 style=\"font-family:&#x27;Playfair Display&#x27;, serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:var(--green-deep);margin-top:2rem;margin-bottom:1rem\">Membership Fees</h3><div style=\"background:rgba(168,149,96,0.06);padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:var(--green-deep);line-height:1.8\"><div>Annual membership fee: <strong>£215</strong></div><div>One-off joining fee: <strong>£100</strong></div></div><p style=\"font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:italic;color:rgba(45,90,61,0.75);margin:0.75rem 0 0\">Fees are payable on acceptance of your application.</p></div><h3 style=\"font-family:&#x27;Playfair Display&#x27;, serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:var(--green-deep);margin-top:2rem;margin-bottom:1rem\">Before you submit, please confirm</h3><label style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;cursor:pointer;margin-bottom:1rem\"><input type=\"checkbox\" required=\"\" style=\"accent-color:var(--gold);width:17px;height:17px;margin-top:3px;flex-shrink:0;cursor:pointer\" name=\"agree_to_fees\"/><span style=\"font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:var(--green-deep);line-height:1.7\">I understand that my application will be reviewed by the Committee, and that — should it be approved — both the £100 joining fee and the £215 annual subscription will become payable.</span></label><label style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;cursor:pointer;margin-bottom:1rem\"><input type=\"checkbox\" required=\"\" style=\"accent-color:var(--gold);width:17px;height:17px;margin-top:3px;flex-shrink:0;cursor:pointer\" name=\"agree_to_annual_fee\"/><span style=\"font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:var(--green-deep);line-height:1.7\">I agree to pay the annual membership fee of £215 each year my membership is renewed, by the deadline set out in the Club Constitution.</span></label><label style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;cursor:pointer;margin-bottom:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\" required=\"\" style=\"accent-color:var(--gold);width:17px;height:17px;margin-top:3px;flex-shrink:0;cursor:pointer\" name=\"agree_to_gdpr\"/><span style=\"font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:var(--green-deep);line-height:1.7\">I understand that Barnes Bowling Club will store m